OL,3,CA36 diversion changed after traffic
OL,4,Cchaos causes 'danger to villagers'
OL,6,FAuthorities in Wiltshire, Bath and
OL,7,FNorth East Somerset have acknowledged
OL,8,Fproblems caused by vehicles avoiding
OL,9,Fofficial A36 diversion routes near
OL,10,FBath.
OL,12,FResidents living in Limpley Stoke have
OL,13,Fbeen warning of the dangers caused by
OL,14,Fthe temporary closure of the A-road -
OL,15,Fwith some calling it "an accident
OL,16,Fwaiting to happen."
