OL,6,FLorries and coaches have since been
OL,7,Ffilmed getting stuck down small roads
OL,8,Fin the village and blocking off
OL,9,Fpavements where children walk to
OL,10,Fschool.
OL,12,FThe A36 is still due to be closed
OL,13,Funtil Spring 2025, but authorities
OL,14,Fhave now made small changes to
OL,15,Fdiversion plans- in the hope of easing
OL,16,Fcongestion.
