OL,6,FNational Highways had said the repairs
OL,7,Fneeded to be urgently undertaken due
OL,8,Fto crumbling foundations, meaning
OL,9,Fmajor structural re-enforcement and a
OL,10,Fnew drainage system.
OL,12,FWiltshire Council is now working
OL,13,Fclosely with both Bath and North East
OL,14,FSomerset Council (B&NES) and National
OL,15,FHighways to ease traffic issues.
