OL,6,FCllr Richard Clewer, leader of
OL,7,FWiltshire Council, said: "We know that
OL,8,Fthe closure of the A36 is causing
OL,9,Ftraffic issues through Limpley Stoke
OL,10,Fand Bradford on Avon, and that's why
OL,11,Fwe're working with both National
OL,12,FHighways and B&NES on these changes to
OL,13,Fthe local road network to improve the
OL,14,Fsituation.
OL,16,F"However, it's important to note that
OL,17,Fthese solutions will not be perfect,
OL,18,Fand there still will be some
OL,19,Fdisruption for the local people, as is
OL,20,Fthe nature of any large-scale highways
OL,21,Fproject.
