OL,6,F"There have also been increases in
OL,7,Ftraffic in other Wiltshire towns and
OL,8,Fvillages, and where we can, we will
OL,9,Fwork with National Highways on this,
OL,10,Fbut there are no easy answers when a
OL,11,Fmajor road is closed, as the A36
OL,12,Fcurrently is."
OL,14,FSean Walsh, route manager for National
OL,15,FHighways, said: "We're working closely
OL,16,Fwith our local authority partners to
OL,17,Fmanage the displaced traffic
OL,18,Fassociated with our A36 closure, while
OL,19,Fseeking to keep the local road network
OL,20,Fsafe and operable.
